The Bearsville Collection Bobby Charles

This CD has the same cover art as the 1994 self-titled album by Bobby Charles (which makes a Golem/Jell), but has 14 songs (the other has 12) and it says "The Bearsville Album" on the spine. The copy I got to work was made in England, ESM CD 675. UPC 5 017615 867527 > (yes that ">" symbol is in the UPC code) This compilation is © Castle Music 1999.

Watermelony has 420 weeks lifespan.
